# Cursor AI Rules for Pomo-Flow

## CRITICAL: Data Safety (TASK-054)

NEVER create demo, sample, or test data programmatically.
NEVER add createSampleTasks(), addDemoData(), seedDatabase(), or similar functions.
NEVER generate "Test Task", "Sample Project", "Demo", or placeholder content.
NEVER create fallback data when database is empty.

Users must see an EMPTY app on first run - not sample data.

## Why

Demo data pollutes real user data and causes confusion.
Previous incidents required manual database cleanup.

## Stack

- Vue 3 + Composition API + TypeScript
- Pinia for state management
- Tailwind CSS with design tokens
- PouchDB for local storage
- Vitest + Playwright for testing

## Key Files

- CLAUDE.md - Full development guidelines
- docs/MASTER_PLAN.md - Project roadmap
- src/stores/tasks.ts - Task management (PROTECTED)

